{
  "id": "a1-present-tense",
  "title": "Present tense (regular verbs)",
  "level": "A1",
  "summary": "Regular verbs add endings to the stem: -e, -st, -t, -en, -t, -en.",
  "sections": [
    {
      "heading": "Conjugation of lernen",
      "body": [
        "Remove -en to get the stem lern-, then add endings.",
        "ich lerne, du lernst, er/sie/es lernt, wir lernen, ihr lernt, sie lernen."
      ],
      "examples": [
        { "de": "Ich lerne jeden Tag.", "en": "I learn every day." },
        { "de": "Du spielst Fußball.", "en": "You play football." }
      ]
    }
  ],
